Name: GeographicLocationSchemeName
Description: A name for the GeographicLocationScheme. May be expressed in multiple languages. Repeat the element to express names with different content, for example different names for different systems.

Name: Label
Description: A display label for the GeographicLocationScheme. May be expressed in multiple languages. Repeat for labels with different content, for example, labels with differing length limitations.

Name: Description
Description: A description of the GeographicLocationScheme. May be expressed in multiple languages and supports the use of Location content.

Name: GeographicLocationSchemeReference
Description: Inclusion of an existing GeographicLocationScheme by reference.

Name: GeographicLocationGroupReference
Description: In-line description of a group of GeographicLocation.
